= First <span style="color: #000000;">**[+ z_party_name +]**</span> Congress

The <span style="color: #000000;">Christian People's Party</span> (<span style="color: #000000;">**[+ z_party_name +]**</span>) has officially been founded! Adam Stegerwald, orchestrator of this arrangement and leader of the former <span style="color: #000000;">Center</span>, has been chosen as the interim leader of the new party.

The <span style="color: #000000;">**[+ z_party_name +]**</span>'s inaugural congress will play a major role in shaping the direction of the newly founded party, and to elect a new chairman. It finally looks like we might have some competition now.

